  "body": "**Problem**: Wrong units for Value when I am on a different Network from Ethereum (i.e. Binance Chain)\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/54408225/181733226-46fe9b8b-31c1-4f9a-a43b-8f537c5e6943.mp4\r\n\r\n1. Go to Remix\r\n2. Unlock MetaMask\r\n3. Change Network for Binance Chain testnet\r\n4. Deploy a contract\r\n5. Include value for a function call\r\n\r\n### Expected Behavior\r\n\r\nValue is represented in the unit of the Network I am connected.\r\n\r\n### Actual Behavior\r\n\r\nValue is always represented in ETH (and its different unit variations)",
